Package: proSCessoR
Type: Package
Title: proSCessoR: Processing of Multimodal Single Cell Datasets
Version: 0.3.0
Author: Constanza Marini-Macouzet
Maintainer: Constanza Marini-Macouzet <cmarinim@fredhutch.org>
Description: proSCessoR contains the functions for CITE-seq (gene and protein expression) and BCR V(D)J data processing as explained in the flowchart. Code is adapted from Aaron Seese's scripts.
    The objective is to process CellRanger data by removing background noise, demultiplexing, identifying multiplets, and capturing complete, productive BCR sequences.
